name: 1st Edition 'G-Shirt' Black with Gold Foil
description:
1st Edition 'G-Shirt.' 

Limited Print with Gold Foil!

The 'G-Shirt' has been "field tested" for durability and wearability. Not only do they look and feel great, but it's got your back no matter what. Unless of course, they've been torn off your back. In that case, you're welcome. Get yourself another shirt!

These shirts are 'Game.' The only question that remains is: are you?

100% Cotton - 100% Game.

DISCLAIMER: Shirt is not pre-shrunk, so expect shrinkage! Get one size bigger! In other words, if you're a medium, get a large! If you're having other "size" issues, we don't sell those products, but we can point you in the right direction.
